# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Table 4: combined in-place bitwise operator absence — all types, all ops
#
# Cross-check: each threading type lacks all three in-place bitwise operators.
# Confirms that the threading API is a synchronization surface only — mutual
# exclusion, signaling, and phase barriers have no bitwise mutation protocol.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

